summary: Whiterun\'s children become teens and get some personality.
descriptionHtml: Whiterun is my home city, it\'s just the right size to live in and feel a part of the community, probably because of the circular districts like the marketplace and around the Gildergreen. I wanted to make the children of whiterun to grow up a little and i also renamed them. I couldn\'t edit Lucia because my creation kit keeps crashing when i try to load Hearthfire DLC.
author: Landon783
